Privacy Policy for BDWASHDATA
1. Introduction
Welcome to BDWASHDATA! This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application published on the Google Play Store.
2. Information We Collect
· Personal Information: We don’t collect personal information, we have pre created user accounts and we provide creadential to users. User just login in app with their credentials.
· Device Information: We may collect your mobile network information.
· Device Location: We may collect your device location for form submission and identify our facilities.
3. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including but not limited to:
· Providing and improving our app's functionality.
· Communicating with you, including responding to your inquiries and providing customer support.
· Analyzing app usage and trends to enhance user experience.
· Personalizing content and recommendations.
· Enforcing our Terms of Service and protecting our rights and interests.
4. Disclosure of Your Information
We may share your information with third parties, including:
· Service providers who assist us in app functionality and analytics.
· Legal authorities when required by law or to protect our rights.
· Business partners or in the event of a business merger, acquisition, or sale.
5. Your Choices
You can control certain aspects of your personal information:
· You may access and update your account information.
· You can opt out of receiving promotional communications from us.
· You can adjust app permissions on your device.
6. Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information; however, no method of transmission over the internet is entirely secure.
7. Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from them.
8. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our data practices. Please review it periodically.
9. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at info@bdwashdata.com